# Copy to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in.
#
# Web3Forms access key for the booking modal. Get one free at https://web3forms.com
# by entering the destination inbox — submissions are forwarded there server-side, so
# the email address never ships in the bundle. The key itself is public by design
# (it only permits sending to the bound inbox), so it being inlined into the client
# build is expected; the env var is for config hygiene, not secrecy.
#
# Must be VITE_-prefixed to be exposed to the client. For the deploy build, set the
# same value as a CI variable (see .github/workflows/firebase-hosting-deploy.yml).
VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
